content.text: The application allows users to change legal data for their firms, providing a secure and efficient platform to manage crucial information. It enables users to update legal documents, amend business details, and ensure compliance with regulatory requirements. The intuitive interface guides users through each step of the process, minimizing errors and streamlining approvals. By leveraging this tool, firms can maintain accurate legal records and swiftly adapt to changing business needs.
Validate user based on user ID
Submit changes to admin (in case of invalid data show note to user)
Show admin if request for changes is valid or needs further action
Send email with PDF for signing.
Show price required to be paid for changes
Gov API that will provide data for firms
Gov API for user checking based on ID number
Backend integration (SupaBase + gov API-s + Payment getaway (without custom pages))
Depends on desing and of of payment provider
Note: In case of developing only frontend without backend estimate can change since we are unaware of how backend will function.
